ta-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/06049\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">06049-HK</a>)</td><td>30.80</td><td>+0.82</td></tr><tr><td>碧桂園服務(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:06098:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/06098\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">06098-HK</a>)</td><td>6.72</td><td>+1.97</td></tr><tr><td>恒大物業(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:06666:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/06666\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">06666-HK</a>)</td><td>0.67</td><td>+1.52</td></tr><tr><td>綠城管理(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:09979:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/09979\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">09979-HK</a>)</td><td>2.67</td><td>+0.38</td></tr></table></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　(ed)</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\"></p></section></main>",
